<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>HealthBridge — Clear, Science-Backed Health Education</title>

  <!-- Modern font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    /* =========================
       HealthBridge — Professional UI
       Single-file HTML + CSS (responsive, accessible)
       ========================= */

    :root{
      --bg:#F6FBFF;            /* very light blue */
      --surface:#FFFFFF;
      --muted:#6B7280;
      --text:#04223A;          /* deep navy for text */
      --brand-600:#0E7490;     /* teal-blue */
      --brand-400:#2DD4BF;     /* aqua accent */
      --accent:#0575E6;        /* bright blue accent for CTA */
      --card-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(2,6,23,0.06);
      --radius:14px;
      --max-width:1200px;
      --glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      --focus: 3px solid rgba(5,117,230,0.12);
    }

    /* Basic reset */
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{height:100%}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial;
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(800px 400px at 10% 10%, rgba(46,163,194,0.04), transparent 12%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg), #F1FAFF);
      -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;
      line-height:1.5;
    }

    .wrap{
      max-width:var(--max-width);
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:28px 24px;
    }

    /* Skip link */
    .skip-link{
      position:absolute;left:8px;top:8px;transform:translateY(-100%);
      background:#04223A;color:white;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;
    }
    .skip-link:focus{transform:none;outline:none;box-shadow:var(--focus)}

    /* Header / Nav */
    header.site-header{
      position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.9), rgba(255,255,255,0.75));
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(4,34,58,0.04);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }
    .nav-inner{
      max-width:var(--max-width);
      margin:0 auto;
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;
      justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 20px;
    }

    .brand{
      display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:center;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text);
    }
    .logo-mark{
      width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:12px;
      display:grid;place-items:center;color:white;font-weight:800;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand-600),var(--brand-400));
      box-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(13,148,136,0.12);
      font-size:18px;
    }
    .brand .title{
      line-height:1;
    }
    .brand .title h1{font-size:1.05rem;margin:0}
    .brand .title p{margin:0;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted)}

    nav.primary{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;
    }
    .nav-links{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center}
    .nav-links a{
      text-decoration:none;color:var(--text);padding:8px 10px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;font-size:0.94rem;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover{background:rgba(5,117,230,0.06)}
    .cta{
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),#0ea5e9);
      color:white;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:12px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;box-shadow:0 8px 22px rgba(5,117,230,0.12);
    }

    /* Mobile nav */
    .mobile-toggle{display:none}

    /* Hero */
    .hero{
      margin-top:18px;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px;
      gap:28px;align-items:center;
    }
    .hero-card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95), rgba(255,255,255,0.9));
      border-radius:18px;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(4,34,58,0.04);
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    }
    .herb{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(14,116,144,0.06);color:var(--brand-600);font-weight:700;font-size:0.85rem;
    }
    .hero-card h2{font-size:1.9rem;margin:14px 0 8px;line-height:1.05}
    .hero-card p.lead{margin:0;color:var(--muted);font-size:1rem}

    .hero-actions{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-top:18px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .btn-primary{background:var(--accent);color:white;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:12px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:800;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(5,117,230,0.12)}
    .btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--brand-600);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(14,116,144,0.08);font-weight:700;text-decoration:none}

    /* Hero visual area with science illustration + metric cards */
    .hero-visual{
      display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;align-items:stretch;
    }
    .visual-illustration{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(14,116,144,0.03), rgba(14,116,144,0.02));
      border-radius:14px;padding:18px;border:1px dashed rgba(14,116,144,0.06);
      display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;
    }
    .illustration svg{width:160px;height:120px;flex-shrink:0}
    .metrics{
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px;
    }
    .metric{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff, rgba(255,255,255,0.95));
      border-radius:10px;padding:10px;text-align:center;border:1px solid rgba(4,34,58,0.03);
      box-shadow:0 8px 18px rgba(2,6,23,0.03)
    }
    .metric strong{display:block;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--brand-600)}
    .metric small{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:6px}

    /* Section layout */
    main{padding:26px 0}
    .section{
      display:grid;grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;gap:22px;align-items:start;margin-top:28px;
    }
    .card{
      background:var(--surface);padding:18px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(4,34,58,0.04);box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);
    }
    .section .content h2{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;font-size:1.2rem;margin:0 0 8px}
    .section .content p{color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 14px}

    .topic-grid{
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:14px;
    }
    .topic{
      display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;padding:14px;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff, rgba(255,255,255,0.98));border:1px solid rgba(2,6,23,0.03);
    }
    .topic .icon{
      width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:10px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:white;
      flex-shrink:0;
    }
    .topic h3{margin:0;font-size:1rem}
    .topic p{margin:6px 0 0;color:var(--muted);font-size:0.95rem}

    /* Aside cards */
    .aside .side-card{position:sticky;top:96px;padding:16px;border-radius:12px}

    /* Utility list styles */
    ul.bullets{margin:8px 0 0;padding-left:18px;color:var(--muted)}
    ul.bullets li{margin:10px 0}

    /* Footer */
    footer{margin-top:40px;padding:36px 20px;color:var(--muted);border-top:1px solid rgba(4,34,58,0.03);background:transparent}
    footer .foot-inner{max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:0 24px}
    footer small{color:var(--muted)}

    /* Icons color variants */
    .ic-brand{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand-600),var(--brand-400))}
    .ic-nutrition{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10B981, #60A5FA)}
    .ic-skin{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#F97316, #FCD34D)}
    .ic-tips{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7C3AED,#06B6D4)}
    .ic-first{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#EF4444,#F97316)}

    /* Hover/interaction */
    .topic:hover{transform:translateY(-6px);transition:transform 220ms cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.2,1)}
    .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);transition:transform 180ms ease}
    .cta:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);transition:transform 180ms ease}

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width:980px){
      .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:18px}
      .hero-visual{order:2}
      .section{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .aside .side-card{position:static;top:auto}
      .metrics{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
      nav.primary{display:none}
      .mobile-toggle{display:inline-flex}
      .nav-inner{padding:12px}
    }

    @media (max-width:520px){
      .metric strong{font-size:0.95rem}
      .illustration svg{width:120px;height:86px}
      .metrics{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
    }

    /* Focus ring for accessibility */
    a:focus,button:focus,input:focus{outline:none;box-shadow:var(--focus);border-radius:10px}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>

  <header class="site-header" role="banner" aria-label="Site header">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="HealthBridge home">
        <div class="logo-mark" aria-hidden="true">HB</div>
        <div class="title">
          <h1>HealthBridge</h1>
          <p>Science-backed health education</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <nav class="primary" role="navigation" aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <div class="nav-links" role="menubar" aria-label="Primary links">
          <a role="menuitem" href="#first-aid">First Aid</a>
          <a role="menuitem" href="#nutrition">Nutrition</a>
          <a role="menuitem" href="#skin">Skin Health</a>
          <a role="menuitem" href="#tips">General Tips</a>
        </div>
        <a class="cta" href="#learn">Get Started</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main" class="wrap" role="main">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
      <div class="hero-card" role="region" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
        <span class="herb" aria-hidden="true">Evidence • Practical • Clear</span>
        <h2 id="hero-title">Practical health education — simplified, trustworthy, science-led</h2>
        <p class="lead">HealthBridge turns complex health topics into clear, actionable steps. Learn first aid basics, nutrition fundamentals, skin care science, and everyday health habits.</p>

        <div class="hero-actions" role="group" aria-label="Primary actions">
          <a class="btn-primary" href="#first-aid">First Aid Guide</a>
          <a class="btn-ghost" href="#learn">How We Source Info</a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top:14px;color:var(--muted);font-size:0.95rem">
          Designed for beginners and learners — each topic links to concise, science-referenced explanations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="false">
        <div class="visual-illustration" aria-hidden="true">
          <!-- Simple "science + care" illustration (SVG) -->
          <svg class="illustration" viewBox="0 0 320 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Illustration of health and science">
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="g1" x1="0" x2="1">
                <stop offset="0" stop-color="#2DD4BF"/>
                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#0E7490"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <rect x="6" y="6" width="308" height="188" rx="12" fill="url(#g1)" opacity="0.06"/>
            <g transform="translate(24,20)">
              <circle cx="52" cy="52" r="32" fill="#ffffff" opacity="0.95"/>
              <path d="M52 38v28M38 52h28" stroke="#0E7490" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <rect x="120" y="16" width="110" height="72" rx="8" fill="#fff" />
              <path d="M128 34c10-8 26-8 36 0s26 8 36 0" stroke="#0575E6" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
              <circle cx="90" cy="128" r="28" fill="#fff"/>
              <path d="M82 120c6 6 14 6 20 0" stroke="#0E7490" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </g>
          </svg>

          <div style="flex:1">
            <div style="font-weight:700;color:var(--brand-600)">HealthBridge at a glance</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;font-size:0.95rem">
              Bite-sized lessons, clear visuals, and practical checklists you can use right away.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="metrics" aria-hidden="false">
          <div class="metric" aria-label="Concise lessons">
            <strong>250+</strong>
            <small>Short lessons</small>
          </div>
          <div class="metric" aria-label="Trusted sources">
            <strong>Evidence</strong>
            <small>Summarized sources</small>
          </div>
          <div class="metric" aria-label="Beginner friendly">
            <strong>Beginner</strong>
            <small>Clear, plain language</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <!-- First Aid -->
    <section class="section" id="first-aid" aria-labelledby="fa-title">
      <div class="content card" aria-labelledby="fa-title">
        <h2 id="fa-title">
          <!-- inline icon -->
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" style="margin-right:8px">
            <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="4" fill="url(#faGrad)"></rect>
            <defs><linearGradient id="faGrad" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#EF4444"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#F97316"/></linearGradient></defs>
          </svg>
          First Aid — practical steps that matter
        </h2>
        <p>Quick, safe actions you can take before professional help arrives. These are starter steps — seek emergency services for serious injuries.</p>

        <div class="topic-grid" style="margin-top:14px">
          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="t-bleed">
            <div class="icon ic-first" aria-hidden="true">
              <!-- cross -->
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M10 4h4v6h6v4h-6v6h-4v-6H4v-4h6V4z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="t-bleed">Bleeding</h3>
              <p>Apply direct pressure, raise the limb, and seek urgent care for heavy or uncontrollable bleeding.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="t-choke">
            <div class="icon ic-first" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2v10" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="18" r="3" fill="white"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="t-choke">Choking</h3>
              <p>If someone can't breathe, cough, or speak, call emergency services and give recommended back blows/abdominal thrusts as trained.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="t-burn">
            <div class="icon ic-first" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2C10 6 6 8 6 12a6 6 0 0012 0c0-4-4-6-6-10z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="t-burn">Burns</h3>
              <p>Cool with running water for 10–20 minutes, cover with a sterile dressing, and seek medical help for deep or extensive burns.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="aside">
        <div class="side-card card" role="complementary" aria-label="First aid checklist">
          <h3 style="margin-top:0">Emergency checklist</h3>
          <ul class="bullets" aria-hidden="false">
            <li>Ensure scene safety before helping</li>
            <li>Call emergency services for serious problems</li>
            <li>Focus on airway, breathing, circulation</li>
            <li>Stay calm and communicate clearly</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <!-- Nutrition -->
    <section class="section" id="nutrition" aria-labelledby="nut-title">
      <div class="content card">
        <h2 id="nut-title">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" style="margin-right:8px">
            <defs><linearGradient id="nutGrad" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#10B981"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#60A5FA"/></linearGradient></defs>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="url(#nutGrad)"/>
          </svg>
          Nutrition — simple science for better meals
        </h2>
        <p>Build balanced meals using food groups and practical swaps rather than restrictive rules.</p>

        <div class="topic-grid" style="margin-top:14px">
          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="n-balance">
            <div class="icon ic-nutrition" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2v20" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="n-balance">Plate balance</h3>
              <p>Fill half your plate with vegetables and fruit, a quarter with lean protein, and a quarter with whole grains.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="n-hyd">
            <div class="icon ic-nutrition" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2c2 2.5 6 4 6 8a6 6 0 11-12 0c0-4 4-5.5 6-8z" fill="white"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="n-hyd">Hydration</h3>
              <p>Water is best. Aim for regular sips throughout the day, and limit sugary beverages.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="n-snack">
            <div class="icon ic-nutrition" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M4 20h16" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="n-snack">Smart snacks</h3>
              <p>Choose nutrient-dense snacks like nuts, fruit, yogurt, and whole-grain crackers for steady energy.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="aside">
        <div class="side-card card">
          <h3 style="margin-top:0">Quick tip</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--muted)">Eat a vegetable or salad first to increase fiber intake and improve fullness without adding extra calories.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <!-- Skin Health -->
    <section class="section" id="skin" aria-labelledby="skin-title">
      <div class="content card">
        <h2 id="skin-title">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" style="margin-right:8px">
            <defs><linearGradient id="skinGrad" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#F97316"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#FCD34D"/></linearGradient></defs>
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="4" fill="url(#skinGrad)"/>
          </svg>
          Skin Health — daily routines grounded in science
        </h2>
        <p>Protecting skin is about gentle care, sun safety, and knowing when to consult a clinician.</p>

        <div class="topic-grid" style="margin-top:14px">
          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="s-daily">
            <div class="icon ic-skin" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2c4 4 6 6 6 10a6 6 0 11-12 0c0-4 2-6 6-10z" fill="white"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="s-daily">Daily routine</h3>
              <p>Use a gentle cleanser, moisturize daily, and avoid products that irritate your skin barrier.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="s-sun">
            <div class="icon ic-skin" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 4v2M12 18v2M4 12h2M18 12h2M6 6l1.5 1.5M16.5 16.5L18 18M16.5 7.5L18 6M6 18l1.5-1.5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="s-sun">Sun safety</h3>
              <p>Apply broad-spectrum sunscreen (SPF 30+) daily and reapply when outdoors for prolonged periods.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="topic" aria-labelledby="s-when">
            <div class="icon ic-skin" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2v10" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="17" r="2" fill="white"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="s-when">When to see a clinician</h3>
              <p>Seek care for changing moles, persistent rashes, or signs of infection like heat, pain, or pus.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="aside">
        <div class="side-card card">
          <h3 style="margin-top:0">Diet & skin</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--muted)">Hydration, omega-3s, and antioxidants support skin health; reducing excess sugar and quitting smoking also helps.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <!-- General Health Tips -->
    <section class="section" id="tips" aria-labelledby="tips-title">
      <div class="content card">
        <h2 id="tips-title">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" style="margin-right:8px">
            <defs><linearGradient id="tipsGrad" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#7C3AED"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#06B6D4"/></linearGradient></defs>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="url(#tipsGrad)"/>
          </svg>
          General Health Tips — small changes, big returns
        </h2>
        <p>Consistent, manageable habits are more effective than short-term fixes. Start with one change at a time.</p>

        <div style="margin-top:12px">
          <ul class="bullets" aria-label="General health tips list">
            <li>Move every day — aim for small activity goals (walks, stairs, short workouts).</li>
            <li>Regular sleep schedule — consistent bed/wake times improve recovery and mood.</li>
            <li>Hand hygiene — simple but powerful to reduce infections.</li>
            <li>Mental wellbeing — connect with others, practice breathing or short mindfulness.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="aside">
        <div class="side-card card">
          <h3 style="margin-top:0">Start this week</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--muted)">Pick one goal: add a vegetable to dinner, a 10-minute walk after lunch, or 30 minutes earlier bedtime.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <!-- Learn more -->
    <section id="learn" style="margin-top:28px">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="margin-top:0">How we source information</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted)">Content is distilled from clinical guidelines, public health agencies, and peer-reviewed literature to create concise learning units. This site is educational — it is not a substitute for professional medical advice.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer role="contentinfo">
